    "raw": "<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"kkp\">\n<style>\n.kkp{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}\n.kkp .kkp-lead{font-size:1.18rem;line-height:1.5;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n.kkp .kkp-lead.kkp-kicker{font-weight:700}\n.kkp .kkp-label{font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;opacity:.55;margin:2rem 0 .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1rem}\n.kkp .kkp-card{display:block;border:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:rgba(150,150,160,.05);transition:transform .15s ease,border-color .15s ease}\n.kkp .kkp-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:#e5462e}\n.kkp .kkp-card img,.kkp .kkp-ph{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n.kkp .kkp-ph{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#23232e 0%,#3a2230 100%)}\n.kkp .kkp-txt{padding:.7rem .8rem .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;line-height:1.25}\n.kkp .kkp-sub{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.68;margin-top:.28rem;line-height:1.35}\n.kkp .kkp-cta{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:1.1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);font-size:1.02rem}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a{color:#e5462e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a:hover{text-decoration:underline}\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-lead kkp-kicker\">The tools change every week. The taste behind them doesn't.</p>\n<p class=\"kkp-lead\">This is my running field guide to the generative AI stack. What I actually use, how I wire it together, and how to get real work out of it without the slop.</p>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Workflows and systems</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/04/01/how-to-build-an-ai-second-brain-that-actually-works-for-you/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image-45.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Build an AI second brain\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"k